<h4>Features</h4>
<div>
	<p>The Docker Swarm driver connects to any existing Docker Swarm cluster empowering you to manage and operate that
		cluster in a single pane of glass.
	</p>
	<p>The driver also extends the default functionality that Docker Swarm offers by adding	many features such as:</p>
</div>
